Note on scope:

This MIT license applies to the contents of this repository: the LaTeX source
of the paper, bibliography, reproducibility scripts, installation scripts, and
supporting documentation.

The QOMN runtime itself (the Rust implementation of the DSL, JIT, and standard
library referenced throughout this paper) is distributed in a separate
repository (github.com/condesi/qomn) under the Apache-2.0 license. That
license governs the runtime independently of this paper.
